---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy — ApplianceErrors.com';
const description = 'How ApplianceErrors.com handles cookies, analytics, and third-party advertising data.';
const updated = '2026-06-10';
---
<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose prose-gray">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: {updated}</em></p>

    <p>
      ApplianceErrors.com ("we", "us") operates this website. This policy
      explains what data is collected when you visit, who it's shared with, and
      what choices you have. By using the site you agree to the terms below.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not require you to create an account, and we do not knowingly
      collect personal information directly. The following data may be
      collected automatically when you visit:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>IP address (truncated where possible)</li>
      <li>Browser type, operating system, device type</li>
      <li>Referring URL and pages viewed on this site</li>
      <li>Approximate geographic location (country/region level)</li>
      <li>Cookies and similar identifiers (see below)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
    <p>
      We use cookies and similar storage to keep the site working, measure
      audience size, and serve advertising. Cookie categories:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Strictly necessary</strong> — required for the site to load.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — anonymous traffic measurement (e.g. Google Analytics).</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising</strong> — used by Google AdSense and partner ad networks to serve, frequency-cap, and measure ads.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-party advertising — Google AdSense</h2>
    <p>
      This site is monetised by display advertising served through
      <strong>Google AdSense</strong>. Google and its partners use cookies and
      device identifiers to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Serve ads based on your prior visits to this site or other sites</li>
      <li>Measure ad performance</li>
      <li>Detect and prevent fraud</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting Google's
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ads Settings</a>
      or the
      <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Digital Advertising Alliance opt-out page</a>.
      For more on how Google uses data from sites that use its services, see
      <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's partner-sites policy</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use Google Analytics 4 or a similar privacy-respecting analytics
      tool to understand which pages are most useful. Analytics data is
      aggregated and not used to identify individuals.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Children</h2>
    <p>
      This site is not directed at children under 13 (or 16 in the EEA/UK). We
      do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
    </p>

    <h2>6. EU / UK / California residents</h2>
    <p>
      If you are in the EEA, UK, or Switzerland, advertising and analytics
      cookies are set only after you consent through our cookie consent
      banner, as required by the GDPR and ePrivacy directive. You can change
      or withdraw your consent at any time by clearing site cookies and
      reloading the page.
    </p>
    <p>
      California residents have rights under the CCPA/CPRA, including the right
      to know, delete, and opt out of "sale" or "sharing" of personal
      information. To exercise these rights, email
      <a href="mailto:hello@applianceerrors.com">hello@applianceerrors.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Data retention</h2>
    <p>
      Server access logs are retained for up to 30 days. Analytics retention
      follows the provider's default (typically 14 months for Google Analytics).
      Ad-network data retention is governed by each network's own policy.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Some outbound links — for example to PartSelect, RepairClinic, or Amazon
      — may be affiliate links. We may earn a small commission when you make a
      purchase after clicking, at no additional cost to you. This never
      influences which products or solutions we recommend.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. The "last updated" date at
      the top reflects the most recent revision.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy or your data: <a href="mailto:hello@applianceerrors.com">hello@applianceerrors.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
